Posts.Content: i do have fibrocystic breasts..or fibrocystic "changes" as the doc called it. Its not hard to deal w/ just can be annoying sometimes because they get swollen and painful around ovulation and when my period is coming. my lump esp on my left breast gets a little hard but easy to move.
